# Yazelix direnv configuration
#
# This file enables automatic environment loading when entering this directory,
# dramatically speeding up Yazelix launches by caching the Nix environment.
#
# Setup:
# 1. Install direnv: https://direnv.net/docs/installation.html
# 2. Hook direnv into your shell: https://direnv.net/docs/hook.html
# 3. Run: direnv allow
#
# Performance impact:
# - First load: ~4s (same as normal)
# - Subsequent loads: <100ms (40x faster!)
#
# The environment is automatically reloaded when flake.nix or flake.lock changes.

use flake . --impure
